<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>215</hymn_number>
<key>Ab</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Bawipa nih a facang lo chungah, Riantuan awk a kan auh, Facang zuntu
 kha an tlawm ca-ah, An caan kha a luan cang.

[C1]
   Lunglawm in Bawipa thawngin chuak tuah, Dawtnak velngeihnak he,
   Khamhnak laksawng thenh awk tha bik kha, Mi vialte hngalhter hna.

[V2]
 Sifakmi hna kha lawmhnak chungah, Zaangfah rawldanghnak ah, Bawipa
 nunnak zungzal co awkah, Annih cu run hruai hna.

[C2]
   Lunglawm in Bawipa thawngin chuak tuah, Dawtnak velngeihnak he,
   Khamhnak laksawng thenh awk tha bik kha, Mi vialte hngalhter hna.

[V3]
 Atu thawk in tuan hramthawk cang tuah, A ceu a dih zau lai, A donghnak
 caan kha a tlun tikah, Kan tuan kho ti lai lo.

[C3]
   Lunglawm in Bawipa thawngin chuak tuah, Dawtnak velngeihnak he,
   Khamhnak laksawng thenh awk tha bik kha, Mi vialte hngalhter hna.</lyrics>
<title>BAWIPA AUHNAK CH215</title>
</song>